INSERT INTO bytes.bytes (id, author_id, title, body, code_snippet, language, embedding, type, is_active, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (
  '3d81541d-9fc1-4824-8167-8c3c899f3f8c',
  '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001',
  $escape$tRPC Performance — Batching, Streaming, and Payload Optimization$escape$,
  $escape$tRPC's default setup fires one HTTP request per procedure call. Switching to `httpBatchLink` collapses simultaneous queries into a single POST, slashing round trips and connection overhead without any change to your procedure definitions.

For payload size, replace the default JSON transformer with `superjson`. It handles `Date`, `Map`, `Set`, and `undefined` natively with a compact wire format, and eliminates manual serialization glue on both router and client. Always select only the fields you need in your Prisma queries — returning raw model objects is the fastest way to bloat tRPC responses.

tRPC v11 ships `httpBatchStreamLink`, which streams each procedure's response as it resolves. A batch of three queries no longer blocks on the slowest — fast responses arrive immediately while slower ones continue in-flight.

Use `splitLink` to route subscriptions through `httpSubscriptionLink` (SSE) while queries and mutations use the batch-stream link. This keeps long-lived SSE connections out of the short-lived HTTP pool, eliminating head-of-line blocking across connection types.

Finally, add Express `compression()` middleware or set `compress: true` in your Next.js config — tRPC's JSON payloads compress 60–80% with gzip.$escape$,
  $escape$import { createTRPCClient, splitLink, httpBatchStreamLink, httpSubscriptionLink } from '@trpc/client';
import superjson from 'superjson';
import type { AppRouter } from '../server/router';

const client = createTRPCClient<AppRouter>({
  links: [
    splitLink({
      condition: (op) => op.type === 'subscription',
      true: httpSubscriptionLink({ url: '/api/trpc', transformer: superjson }),
      false: httpBatchStreamLink({
        url: '/api/trpc',
        transformer: superjson,
        maxURLLength: 2048,
      }),
    }),
  ],
});$escape$,
